The '''Algerian Chess Championship''' is currently organized by FADE, the Algerian Chess Federation ({{lang-fr|Fédération Algérienne des échecs}}), which was established in 1973. It joined [[FIDE]] in 1974 and held the first national championships in 1975.<ref name=chessnc>{{cite web |title=Organizations: Algeria |url=http://www.chessnc.com/organizations/item-63.html |website=E-ChessPedia |publisher=Chess Network Company |access-date=2015-05-19}}</ref>
