==Fan-voted openers== {{unreferenced section|date=June 2012}} In 2011, the Summer Slaughter Tour offered their fans the opportunity to vote on who would open the tour. The choices for 2011 were [[Dawn Of Ashes]], [[Revocation]], [[Neuraxis]], [[Conducting From The Grave]], [[The Contortionist]], [[Within The Ruins]], [[Volumes (band)|Volumes]], [[Augury]], [[7 Horns 7 Eyes]], [[Rings of Saturn (band)|Rings of Saturn]], and Struc/tures. [[Within the Ruins]] ultimately received the most votes and thus won the opening spot for the tour. That same year [[Conducting From The Grave]], The Contortionist, Rings of Saturn, Volumes, and Struc/tures all toured together on what was billed as the Slaughter Survivors Tour. This tour also included [[Scale the Summit]], who had not been part of the voting.
For the 2012 edition of the Summer Slaughter Tour, fans were once again given the chance to vote on the opening act. The choices for 2012 were [[Aegaeon (band)|Aegaeon]], [[Battlecross]], [[Cerebral Bore]], [[Enfold Darkness]], [[Fallujah (band)|Fallujah]], [[Fit For An Autopsy]], [[Hour of Penance]], [[I Declare War (band)|I Declare War]], [[Pathology (band)|Pathology]], and [[Vildhjarta]]. The opening slot for the 2012 tour went to Cerebral Bore, and Pathology, Enfold Darkness, Fallujah, Fit For An Autopsy, and Aegaeon also joined the 2012 Slaughter Survivors Tour.
The choices for the 2013 tour were [[Abiotic (band)|Abiotic]], [[As They Burn]], [[Dark Sermon]], [[Erra (band)|Erra]], Fit For An Autopsy, [[Howl (American band)|Howl]], [[Intervals (band)|Intervals]], [[Into The Flood (band)|Into the Flood]], [[King Conquer]], [[Last Chance To Reason]], [[My Bitter End]], [[Nekrogoblikon (band)|Nekrogoblikon]], Rings Of Saturn, [[Syqem]], [[Soreption]], [[Today I Caught the Plague]], and [[Thy Art Is Murder]]. Thy Art Is Murder was the chosen band. However, since they were nearly tied with Rings of Saturn by a few votes, the organizers decided to put both Rings of Saturn and Thy Art Is Murder on the bill. [[Vektor (band)|Vektor]] were put on the initial ballot by their record label without the band's knowledge or approval, and upon discovering this, had to withdraw due to incompatible scheduling. The Slaughter Survivors Tour didn't occur in 2013, and didn't return in 2014 either.
Summer Slaughter 2014 didn't see the tour offer an opportunity to vote on openers; rather, the opener was chosen by Headbang for the Highway showcase, and Boreworm was selected. [[Mayhem Festival]] also uses the Headbang for the Highway showcase to select bands.
